            "text": "{\"action\": \"next\", \"messages\": [{\"id\": \"abfeb97d-ecf2-4cbe-b18c-493e14ff9679\", \"author\": {\"role\": \"user\"}, \"create_time\": 1776096904.0840619, \"content\": {\"content_type\": \"text\", \"parts\": [\"You are a tool-capable assistant.\\n\\nYou must respond using only the following XML-like tags:\\n- <think>...</think>\\n- <tool_calls>[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"ToolName\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{...}}]</tool_calls>\\n- <final_answer>...</final_answer>\\n\\nRules:\\n- You may output one or more <think> blocks.\\n- You must then output exactly one terminal block: either <tool_calls> or <final_answer>.\\n- Do not output any text outside these tags.\\n- In <tool_calls>, the content must be a valid JSON array. Each item must be an object with keys \\\"name\\\" and \\\"arguments\\\".\\n- If you need only one tool, still use <tool_calls> with an array of length 1.\\n- In string values inside <tool_calls>, you must escape quotes, backslashes, and newlines exactly as JSON requires.\\n- After </tool_calls> or </final_answer>, stop immediately.\\n- Never generate Observation, tool results, or a second terminal block in the same response.\\n- Never output <observation>; the system will provide tool results in the next turn.\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Available tools\\n\\n- mcp__yapi__get-project-detail(): \\u83b7\\u53d6\\u9879\\u76ee\\u8be6\\u60c5\\n- mcp__yapi__get-interfaces(projectId: number (required), catid: number, page: number, limit: number): \\u83b7\\u53d6\\u63a5\\u53e3\\u5217\\u8868\\n- mcp__yapi__get-interface-detail(interfaceId: number (required)): \\u83b7\\u53d6\\u63a5\\u53e3\\u8be6\\u60c5\\n\\nSystem\\uff1aCurrent model: gpt-4o\\nCurrent date: 2026-04-14\\n Additional info for this conversation: \\n\\nYou are a helpful assistant. You can help me by answering my questions. You can also ask me questions.\\n**User**: \\u5e2e\\u6211\\u770b\\u770b\\u6211\\u7684yapi\\u4e2d\\u6709\\u591a\\u5c11\\u63a5\\u53e3 (\\u4e25\\u683c\\u5de5\\u5177\\u534f\\u8bae\\u6a21\\u5f0f;\\u5982\\u9700\\u8c03\\u7528\\u5de5\\u5177, \\u53ea\\u80fd\\u8f93\\u51fa <think> \\u4e0e\\u4e00\\u4e2a\\u7ec8\\u7ed3\\u5757\\u6807\\u7b7e, \\u7ec8\\u7ed3\\u5757\\u53ea\\u80fd\\u662f <tool_calls> \\u6216 <final_answer>, \\u7981\\u6b62\\u8f93\\u51fa\\u6807\\u7b7e\\u5916\\u6587\\u672c\\u6216\\u66ff\\u4ee3\\u65b9\\u6848)\"]}, \"metadata\": {\"selected_github_repos\": [], \"selected_all_github_repos\": false, \"serialization_metadata\": {\"custom_symbol_offsets\": []}}}], \"parent_message_id\": \"client-created-root\", \"model\": \"auto\", \"client_prepare_state\": \"success\", \"timezone_offset_min\": 480, \"timezone\": \"Europe/Berlin\", \"conversation_mode\": {\"kind\": \"primary_assistant\"}, \"enable_message_followups\": true, \"system_hints\": [], \"supports_buffering\": true, \"supported_encodings\": [\"v1\"], \"client_contextual_info\": {\"is_dark_mode\": true, \"time_since_loaded\": 300, \"page_height\": 600, \"page_width\": 1200, \"pixel_ratio\": 2, \"screen_height\": 982, \"screen_width\": 1512, \"app_name\": \"chatgpt.com\"}, \"paragen_cot_summary_display_override\": \"allow\", \"force_parallel_switch\": \"auto\"}"
